title: Mary Gold Sex Hormone'd Druggie mixtape
description:

3.- Lisa produced by Diggable Slim 
4.- Fukk feat. Leaf produced by Crack Tracks 
5.- Druggie Girl by Dirty Spice produced by Negrosaki 
6.- Threesome produced by L.A. Beatz 
7.- Miley Cyrus produced by Nesby Phips 
8.- Coup De Ville produced by Rmur 
9.- Grand Theft produced by Diggable Slim 
10.- Needy produced by Lu B 
11.- Treetop Express produced by Diggable Slim 
12.- Prayer feat. Curren$y produced by Lachase x DVN 
13.- Steezus Christ produced by Junedocc
